This glassware shows images of my favorite Doctor Who with text.

Voice Commands

    Launch static card viewer

        "ok glass" ... "show my doctor"

    Launch live card viewer

        "ok glass" ... "long live the doctor"

Live card handling adapted from the compass example:

    https://github.com/googleglass/gdk-compass-sample

